{
  "stem": "25639.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then, if we had a small hands, then we were picked to do this work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And having been young at the time, having had small hands, I qualified to work with this small precision instrument.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I learned about this process actually later.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I've talked about this procedure, but I didn't know that this was to be for the work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So it took me really years afterwards, when I ran into a German person who was working on his PhD and his subject was Hitler's underground factories and I asked-- he wanted to interview me while I was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And in return I asked him for a favor, to share some information about it with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "When I learned that he also did the Beendorf underground factories, I certainly [LAUGHS] raised an ear or an eyebrow.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And-- and I was most grateful to him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we are in touch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this man who trained me was very kind, very kind to me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he sometimes shared part of his lunch with me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was a tremendously courageous act, because the slightest infraction was punishable by a bullet through the head.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was top secret.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, I might add here that [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] a few years ago when I returned to Germany, to another camp to-- to-- that I haven't talked about yet, I was interviewed by a reporter in Germany.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it appeared in the German newspapers, apparently, because the person who interviewed me forwarded an article to me-- well, the article to me, as well as a letter from someone in Germany.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This little lady is in her 90s, around the mid-90s.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she read the story about Beendorf and that the civilian trainer shared his lunch with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
